istreatment of a minor rotondo no longer works for tahoe resources the seven men who were shot filed a civil lawsuit garcia v tahoe resources inc against tahoe resources in june  alleging that rotondo ordered the shooting and that tahoe resources was legally responsible for the shooting the suit alleged assault aggravated assault and obstruction of justice and that the shooting was premeditated on november   the supreme court of british columbia stayed a judgment in favor of tahoe resources key peopleedit kevin mcarthur founder and executive chair ron clayton president and chief executive officer elizabeth mcgregor vice president and chief financial officer brian brodsky vp exploration tom fudge vp operations edie hofmeister vp corporate affairs charles v muerhoff vp technical services mark sadler vp projects development mark utting vp investor relations peter van alphen vp operations timmins board of directorsedit kevin mcarthur executive chair ron clayton president  chief executive officer director a dan rovig lead director tanya jakusconek drago kisic alan c moon paul b sweeney james s voorhees kenneth f williamson dr klaus zeitler officesedit vancouver canada reno nevada usa lima peru guatemala city guatemala toronto canada see alsoedit companies portal escobal mine referencesedit  about tahoe resouces inc  tahoe resources inc new leader in precious metals wwwtahoeresourcescom   management team  tahoe resources inc new leader in precious metals wwwtahoeresourcescom   a b c d e taho income statement  tahoe resources inc ordinary stock  yahoo finance financeyahoocom   jamasmie cecilia feb   tahoe resources adds canadian gold mines to portfolio by buying lake shore miningcom retrieved sep     tahoe resources annual information form for the year ended december   pdf tahoeresourcescom tahoe resources inc march   retrieved march     investor faqs  tahoe resources inc new leader in precious metals wwwtahoeresourcescom retrieved    tahoe resources  more violence in guat